            "access": {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "access",
                "text": "Characters from Absalom, New Thassilon, Alkenstar, Dongun Hold, or especially technological regions of Arcadia like the Deadshot Lands have access to uncommon clockwork items from the first two chapters of this book. Uomoto  characters,  characters  from  Eihlona, automatons with memories of Jistka, and Arcadians all have access to uncommon magitechnological options from the first two chapters of this book."
            },
